      <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">A burst pipe releases 400 litres of water per hour. The steps you take in the first 10 minutes determine how much damage your property suffers. Read this before an emergency happens.</p>
      <div class="blog-meta">
        <span><strong>By</strong> Ideal Plumbing Solutions</span>
